
#Apache Flume
Tutorial for setting up flume with log4j http://www.thecloudavenue.com/2013/11/using-log4jflume-to-log-application.html

Keep following things in mind
1. Allow the ports for flume agents in azure portal
2. Take care of conf/yarn-env.sh
2. Start hdfs and yarn before starting flume
3. Start flume agent using
4. 

